Chakra UI is a popular open-source React component library that provides a set of accessible and customizable UI components for building web applications. 


npx create-react-app . --template @chakra-ui  -> use to install chakra UI.
npm i react-responsive-carousel -> fro carousel purpose.
import {ChakraProvider} from "@chakra-ui/react"
<ColorModeScript/>
    <ChakraProvider  theme={theme} >
    <ColorModeSwitcher />
    <App />
    </ChakraProvider>


we can easily export the methods of chakraUI directly in jsx file
eg:- import{
    Drawer,
  DrawerBody,
  DrawerHeader,
} from '@chakra-ui/react';
now we can call this in return block with some attributes like isOpen onClose
 "Drawer" is a UI component that is commonly used for creating slide-out panels or menus that can be toggled open and closed. 
DrawerOverlay is used to create a translucent overlay that covers the entire screen when the drawer is open.



